data.description: One of the larger homes in Vicksburg Village with 2362 sq ft. Light and bright w/Newer flooring in LR, DR and BDs. Bedrooms are good sized. Kitchen is spacious w/Island, Lots of cabinets, Eat-in area, and Window seat. Floor to ceiling Brick Woodburning fireplace in living room.Formal dining area. 2 Extra rooms in this home for Office, Crafting, Exercising, Storage, etc. Large utility room big enough to have extra refrigerator or freezer. Sunroom that could be an additional living space that's not included in the sqft. Covered front patio & Low maintenance landscaping----HOA Fees take care of front yard and offers Club house w/Many activities, Indoor swimming pool, Library area, Pool table, & Full kitchen!! It's a must see!
